# pexip_infinity_identity_provider_attribute (Resource)

Manages an identity provider attribute with the Infinity service. Identity provider attributes define custom attributes that can be mapped from identity providers for user authentication and authorization.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "pexip_infinity_identity_provider_attribute" "example" {
  name        = "department"
  description = "Department attribute from identity provider"
}
```


